reviewText: Its a cool show about Big Daddy Don Garlits this  is a must for any fan of DragRacing or DareDevil  s where most of the famous DareDevils start out  is at the DragStrip. Don Garlits tells his life  why and how he wanted to  build the rearengine  dragster. If you allways wanted to know that then  this tape is for you.
